summary: This appears to be a law enforcement lieutenant's daily activity report for July 28, 2019, referencing the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York. The document is part of the Jeffrey Epstein case records and is marked as confidential by the SDNY.

events.title: Lieutenant's Daily Activity Report
events.description: A lieutenant filed a daily activity report, which is part of the confidential records from the Southern District of New York related to the Epstein case.

keyFacts: The document is a lieutenant's log and daily activity report dated July 28, 2019.
It is marked as confidential and part of the Southern District of New York (SDNY) Epstein case records.
The report references the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC), where Jeffrey Epstein was held.
The document's file name and reference number (EFTA00139694) indicate it is part of a larger set of released case documents.
The text is partially garbled or redacted, limiting the extraction of specific details about activities or individuals.
